Interface EventSubscriber

  • All Superinterfaces:
    akka.actor.Actor, akka.actor.ActorLogging
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    JEventSubscriber

    public interface EventSubscriber
extends akka.actor.Actor, akka.actor.ActorLogging
    Adds the ability to subscribe to events. The subscribed actor will receive Event messages for the given prefix.
